From 0925add90542e283beb842fd0eccbbcf2d383d7a Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Claude <assistant@local>
Date: Sat, 27 Jun 2026 13:08:15 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] feat(ldl): LDL foundation, semantic migration, and
 LedgerCollapsingHero

Squashed: Commit A (LDL foundation), Commit B (dashboard migration),
and the Living Hero (collapsing scroll-driven hero).

Includes: LedgerColors with surface levels and financial semantics via
CompositionLocal, LedgerTheme as the single LDL entry point, LedgerSurface
and LedgerHairline primitives, LedgerBorder and LedgerOpacity tokens,
LedgerCard deleted, all dashboard components repointed from Material
colorScheme to LedgerTheme.colors, DashboardScreen rebuilt on Box +
LazyColumn + LedgerCollapsingHero overlay with scroll-driven transformation,
snap behavior (experimental), KDoc on every new primitive.
